■ Block
  name⦂ Head
  value⦂ String

  ▶ new
  ⏺ name⦂ Head
    @ name, "}"

  ▶ new
  ⏺ name⦂ Head
  ⏺ value⦂ String
    @name: name
    @value: value

  ▶ equals⦂ boolean
  ⏺ name⦂ Head
  ⏺ value⦂ String
    ⏎ @name = name
    ∧ @value ≈ value

≣ Head
  ANONYM    · Anonymous Function or Class, or inner scope
  CONSTANTS · Constants for enum constants
  CLASS     · Class for constructor name
  SELECTION · Selection head for cases
  CASE      · Case for break or fallthrough
